title: The Jam - Urban Adventure (1993 Series)-Dark Horse-Bernie Mireau
description:
The Dark Horse run of 'The Jam: Urban Adventure' . Three issues spanning three years it's no wonder the series didn't take off but a great series nonetheless.

 Bernie Mireault's 'Jammer' is one of the most creative and engaging takes on life and super-heroics in years. It's a refreshing combination of adventure and pathos that is neither cliche nor a spoof. The Jam is an original.

 ENJOY

 The Caliber Press run will be coming soon...
